# IPL Dashboard React App

This is a React-based web application that displays IPL teams, their recent matches, and match details. It uses a public API to fetch IPL data and showcases each team's latest matches and performance.

## Features

- Homepage listing all IPL teams
- Team page showing:
  - Team banner
  - Latest match details
  - Recent matches
- Responsive design with React Router-based navigation
- Error handling for invalid routes (404 Page)

## Tech Stack

- React
- React Router DOM
- CSS
- Public API from CCBP
